Ralph BLACK et al. v. Tom KOCH. No. 7157. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Jan. 23, 1963. Malcolm Miller, Wichita, Kan., and James A. Williams, Dodge City, Kan., for appellants. H. Lee Turner and J. Eugene Balloun, Great Bend, Kan., for appellee.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and ARRAJ, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed January 23, 1963, pursuant to stipulation of counsel.
